---
/**
 * TheWay — Act III
 * Return to light with improved readability - cards on semi-transparent background
 */
---

<section 
  id="the-way" 
  class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Full-bleed background image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img 
      src="/farm-sunrise.png" 
      alt="Pastoral farm at sunrise"
      loading="lazy"
      class="way-image w-full h-full object-cover "
    />
    <!-- Stronger overlay for readability -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#F2F0E9]/70 via-[#F2F0E9]/60 to-[#F2F0E9]"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 min-h-screen flex items-center py-24 md:py-32 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section header -->
      <h2 class="way-line text-center font-['Cormorant_Garamond',serif] text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-[#2B2B2B] mb-12 md:mb-16">
        Here's how we do it differently.
      </h2>
      
      <!-- Content cards for better readability -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="way-line bg-[#F2F0E9]/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-[#2B2B2B]/5">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-['EB_Garamond',serif] text-[#2B2B2B]">
            <span class="text-[#C8A97E] font-semibold">Real pasture, not a marketing term.</span><br/>
            Our birds live outside on open grass—not in a barn with a "pasture access" door that most never use.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="way-line bg-[#F2F0E9]/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-[#2B2B2B]/5">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-['EB_Garamond',serif] text-[#2B2B2B]">
            <span class="text-[#C8A97E] font-semibold">Moved to fresh grass daily.</span><br/>
            Every morning, we move the flock to new pasture where they forage for insects, clover, and seeds—the diet they evolved to eat.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="way-line bg-[#F2F0E9]/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-[#2B2B2B]/5">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-['EB_Garamond',serif] text-[#2B2B2B]">
            <span class="text-[#C8A97E] font-semibold">You can taste the difference.</span><br/>
            Deep, rich flavor. Golden fat. The kind of chicken your grandmother remembers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


